videos.description: USC's Elijah Stewart finishes the fast-break with a dunk assisted by De'Anthony Melton.
videos.headline: USC's Elijah Stewart throws down a 2-handed dunk in transition

videos.description: USC's Shaqquan Aaron uses a spin move to find enough room to get off a shot after he's fouled.
videos.headline: USC's Shaqquan Aaron hits a ridiculous and-one shot

videos.description: USC's Chimezie Metu gets fouled on a made lay-up to bring USC within single digits after trailing by 23 points.
videos.headline: USC pulls within single digits

videos.description: Arizona's Lauri Markkanen nails a deep 3-Pointer off the glass and USC's Jordan McLaughlin answers with a lay-up seconds later to leave Arizona's lead at 70-66.
videos.headline: Arizona and USC trade baskets in the final minute of a close game
